to update:

on power shell:

git add .
git commit -m "restore missing /admin route"
git push

on pythonanywhere bash:
cd SummerPointsGame
git pull


to update challenges: run the update_challenges script

wipe db in bash:
cp database.db database.db.backup
rm database.db

discard local edits to overwrite to prevent merge failure/abortion:
git checkout -- app.py


replace the db to overwrite:
cp database.db database.db.backup
mv database.db database.db.livebackup
rm database.db
mv database.db.livebackup database.db


Stop tracking uploads + db:
in bash:
cd C:\Users\munch\OneDrive\Desktop\SummerApp
git rm --cached database.db

in powershell:
git add .gitignore
git commit -m "stop tracking database.db and uploads"
git push